        <item>
            <title>1.2.8</title>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://getsetcraft.com/release-notes</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 20:08:24 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.8</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changes

- Editing a metaset's master song no longer drops its members from the builder.
- The PRO Report opens the native print dialog, with a preview and save-as-PDF,
  instead of doing nothing or opening a browser window.
- The printed Tech Cue Sheet uses a larger, more readable font.

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/brianhaggis/setcraft-website/releases/download/v1.2.8/Setcraft.dmg" length="68680937" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="ho0ykttpmPPdnnIy2sBsa4oYptW55eUCT4T6lb5J7P+KyXNOAb4vFztpJI3Zx5ke6+aQY2rdgxE6Fs66h7QwDA=="/>
