        <item>
            <title>1.2.7</title>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://getsetcraft.com/release-notes</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 18:08:32 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.7</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changes

- Tech Cue Sheets now show the songs inside a medley, each with its own FOH and
  Lighting notes.
- The cue sheet's back link returns to the setlist instead of a blank page.
- The PRO Report opens in its own window with a working Print button.
- Report a Bug now writes to hello@getsetcraft.com.

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/brianhaggis/setcraft-website/releases/download/v1.2.7/Setcraft.dmg" length="67103356" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="MgMxM1OiW4/KBtFP+0ds65cjeWJnVlfbjU6BjzCGEYRSu2akMYlQszoFNdhBjBukNVT8mchhP5d/I0MiPKB2Aw=="/>
