            <sparkle:version>1.2.5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changes

- Internal licensing cleanup: the app is now built entirely from permissive
  open-source components, and ships a smaller download as a result.
- Added an Open-Source Licenses page (About panel, Help menu, and Backstage).

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
