        <item>
            <title>1.2.4</title>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://getsetcraft.com/release-notes</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 18:54:35 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's new

**1.2.4**

- Help > About now opens the About panel.
- Removed the unused macOS window tab bar.

**1.2.3**

- Tutorial wording fixes: exploring the demo band, cover songs, and backups.

**1.2.2**

- Lyric and chart books now print, not just export to PDF.
- Photo Import no longer shows "Setlist created" before you import anything.
- Account & License shows your license status and activated artist profiles.
- The Shows list gains a PRO Report link, and the tutorials were reviewed for
  accuracy with new walkthroughs.

**1.2.1**

- Title-cased the navigation and page labels.

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/brianhaggis/setcraft-website/releases/download/v1.2.4/Setcraft.dmg" length="106070571" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="46W+KH+V++JxHetGc1vnQhZ2SUG6nGYtiHKeo5MP2ePYcOEpy/UTKuoIVA7cqV9oCYaXiIn5RINQQE1Dot3PBw=="/>
        </item>
