        <item>
            <title>1.2.2</title>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://getsetcraft.com/release-notes</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 17:03:23 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changes

- Lyric and chart books now print, not just export to PDF.
- Photo Import no longer shows "Setlist created" before you import anything.
- Account & License shows your license status and activated artist profiles.
- The Shows list gains a PRO Report link on each show with a setlist.
- Tutorials reviewed for accuracy, with new walkthroughs for lyrics and charts,
  show filtering, saving, and a Backup & Restore tour.

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
